{"tid":1153871,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"爆竹聲特效 Red Velvet Joy(牙災)嚇到掩耳跑走冇再上台","createTime":"2019-05-14T02:09:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T02:34:52.000Z","uid":152123,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"231688422a3bbf3038eb54b04ca074581c2edc9a","tid":1153871,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:09:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Twe-nWAKHGg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTwe-nWAKHGg&d=4exhEwVElvs0p929i6aHTzQMt3kYY8c646%2Bk6hbI14w%3D&h=ae598ac3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Twe-nWAKHGg</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓女團Red Velvet的成員Joy在表演結束發生異狀，疑似因為被煙火聲音嚇到，整個臉部糾結、摀著耳朵非常不舒服，她管不了還沒打完招呼，就匆忙往後跑並蹲坐在舞台邊，讓現場觀眾與成員都嚇了一跳，她事後感到非常抱歉，在IG發文解釋曾發生的事件造成她內心陰影。<br />\n<br />\nRed Velvet在昨（11日）晚間受邀參與一燒酒品牌舉辦的公演，半小時內表演了包含《Red Flavor》、《Power Up》等夯曲，其中在最後一首《RBB》表演完後，現場放起祝賀煙火，但Joy開始出現異常反應！<br />\n<br />\nJoy聽到爆炸先是嚇了一跳，接下來臉部糾結痛苦，她趕緊摀住耳朵，在成員都還在Ending Pose的時候，她已經受不了而往後台衝，最後摀著耳朵蹲坐在舞台邊，她一邊喘著氣，可看見工作人員輕撫她的肩膀安撫她的情緒。由於舞台上突然缺一個人，觀眾安可喊一半也不知所措，Red Velvet便在主持人圓場下一起離開舞台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z9J5TDq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz9J5TDq.png&h=40856f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有網友拍到Joy出狀況的驚險一幕，瞬間在網路上瘋傳，粉絲擔心她出事，她也在Red Velvet的官方IG上報平安了。她解釋，「因為以前曾經有爆竹就在眼前炸開，而對爆竹感到害怕，而今天在沒預料的狀況之下，甚至產生了耳鳴，而導致最後無法好好的道別，真的很抱歉，現在已經沒事了。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JsV4pLq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJsV4pLq.png&h=5973a211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實表演中間Joy（右二）就先被爆炸聲嚇過一次，張大嘴驚恐尖叫。（圖／翻攝自YouTube／Sleeppage）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmx2VSh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcmx2VSh.png&h=3fdb9971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而事實上Joy在同場表演的稍早之前，也被突然炸開的彩帶特效與爆竹聲音給嚇到，她驚嚇到嘴巴張超級大、甚至發出驚恐尖叫，發瘋狂抖似的往後退了好幾步，並摀著耳朵十分害怕。這時旁邊的瑟琪見狀趕緊安撫她，只是因為這發煙火較短暫，她很快就平復情緒，沒想到最後再度被嚇到。"},{"pid":"c37d32688be02b49b387bd253bb9ed0e3434cd77","tid":1153871,"uid":253005,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42c5f50f97f5e436df35cf0fe0b6ae0c6f81ff5f","tid":1153871,"uid":152123,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c37d32688be02b49b387bd253bb9ed0e3434cd77","tid":1153871,"uid":253005,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:11:26.000Z","msg":"人體爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7eed3445f62ad92e81b752c4b7424906a7ecf5","tid":1153871,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"好想保護佢"},{"pid":"dd7e84fadaacc9485b7a8093d6eb68a40ec98c50","tid":1153871,"uid":138138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:13:13.000Z","msg":"最後張圖用照妖鏡影<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f08290e26fe52c7bab5406e3c17be035d99e41","tid":1153871,"uid":152123,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f7eed3445f62ad92e81b752c4b7424906a7ecf5","tid":1153871,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:12:32.000Z","msg":"好想保護佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6ze49eA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6ze49eA.png&h=b4fb258a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個工作人員就爽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5815770d65ac4a3b5b0af84fda931ddc019574e3","tid":1153871,"uid":129660,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c37d32688be02b49b387bd253bb9ed0e3434cd77","tid":1153871,"uid":253005,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:10:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:16:38.000Z","msg":"芝士腸爆汁好出奇咩"},{"pid":"bf1599bfbc8112f24b81a12a3cc91dca583fad72","tid":1153871,"uid":91238,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"最尾張圖，全部人塊面都好膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10f6d6dc961a68db52994391bf744d533ac70b0b","tid":1153871,"uid":80814,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"佢唔係第一次被煙花效果嚇親<br />\n同埋佢係嚇到都控制唔到自己要跑走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29303bf18920e55aa12cdbfb7740cf34953f06e7","tid":1153871,"uid":34071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:20:39.000Z","msg":"心痛死牙永<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牙永實問點解出事果個係牙災而唔係老女人牙現"},{"pid":"cdc6e985c269301bbfd51bfad8568557f71af5a8","tid":1153871,"uid":35639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1CGSyJc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1CGSyJc.png&h=a49e81a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36ceff830b0970443a4186008a06c06807ca1ef2","tid":1153871,"uid":27664,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:22:14.000Z","msg":"其他成員：你做多咗啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7578ef9debe12e75a5c8596f76c7f0d04308cb3","tid":1153871,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"係咪岸撚鳩架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9cbe96a6dbd90176253d2d2e72d81a92a3acbe7","tid":1153871,"uid":171598,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T02:34:52.000Z","msg":"扮咩撚野"}]}